findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeAccount() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the excluded list and evaluate total supply, respectively. These functions may be aborted with an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges
findings.description: The owner has excessive privileges to change tax and liquidity fee, maximum transaction amount, and exclude from fees, which can lead to unintended consequences.
